# lucario Theme Demo
Output examples/svgs/themes/lucario.svg

Set Theme lucario
Set Template macos
Set Title "lucario"
Set FontSize 14

Type "echo 'Welcome to the lucario theme!'"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "echo 'This is how your terminal looks.'"
Sleep 200ms
Left 21
Shift+Right 4
Sleep 400ms
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 1s
